{"tid":925754,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 -方魚肉碎蠔仔粥","createTime":"2018-12-03T03:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T14:48:57.000Z","uid":30742,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"94c7ee0e95ea722537afd34a1fc92671f707126d","tid":925754,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXPdVQH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXPdVQH.jpg&h=aff0c0a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LtU9s0ZE8k8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLtU9s0ZE8k8&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732Tf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8bdbeca2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LtU9s0ZE8k8</a><br />\n<br />\n上年同fd行山入大澳見到有一檔有原條大地魚買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即時入手幾條，放左係雪櫃<br />\n本身係想磨大地魚粉，但又無左回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁岩見到街市d蠔仔幾大粒，就拎左條出黎煲粥<br />\n自己煲就可以有咁濃煲咁濃，最後只係落左dddd鹽已經好夠味！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過蠔仔可以再多d，咁會仲正！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜 <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/11/congee-with-minced-pork-dried-flounder.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fcongee-with-minced-pork-dried-flounder.html&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732Tf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3d78d8f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/11/congee-with-minced-pork-dried-flounder.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732Tf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=87f41052\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732Tf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0433ea25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732Tf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f28c5f13\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"561c988f211462ea3c9b48c8ee11bcd60263a4fb","tid":925754,"uid":50642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ed11e57eed7b5f36552dab30a698d3ec2444c0","tid":925754,"uid":149357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"蠔仔粥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbf95d36de2fd50c863e5ab919163a4cec81f07","tid":925754,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"561c988f211462ea3c9b48c8ee11bc